  2. U7 siuN7 hit-e5 lang5 chaiN2-iuN7 beh eng7 hit chit8-khou-gin5 . Hit-e5 gin5 sui-jian5 si7 chiau3 kong-to7 tit-tioh8, chong2-si7 be7-tit-thang chhin3-chhai2 eng7 . Lam7-sam2 khai-gin5 u7 kui2-na7 khoan2 , chiong5-tiong thang kong2 , -- phoa3-chiN5, eng7-gong7-chiN5 , poah8-kiau2 , than3 su-iok8 , chhia-hoa5 , pou3-lou7-lang5, hai7 pat8-lang5 , li7-ek ka-ti7 na7-tiaN7 . Lun7-kau3 liau2-chiN5 u7 iau3-kin2 e5 pun2-hun7 kap toa7 e5 koan-he7 . Lang5 m7-thang phah-sng3 in-ui7 i sou2 u7-e5 si7 kong-gi7 e5 chiN5 , sou2-i2 thang chhut-chai7 i eng7 . Hit-ho7 chiN5 si7 na2-chhin-chhiuN7 tui3 Siong7-te3 lai5 , si7 Siong7-te3 kau-tai7--e5 . An2-ni-seN , lang5 eng-kai tioh8 chiau3 Siong7-te3 e5 i3-su3 lai5 khai , in-ui7 kau3 pat8-jit8 Siong7-te3 beh chha5-siau3. U7 che7-che7 ho2-giah8 e5 lang5 tui3 i-e5 chiN5-chai5 siu7-tioh8 toa7-hai7 , iah8 u7 che7-che7 song3-hiong lang5 tui3 i-e5 bo5 sim2-mih8 chiN5 siu7-tioh8 toa7 li7-ek . U7-chiN5 e5 lang5 tioh8 the2-thiap8 bo5-chiN5--e5, na7 bo5, be7 bian2-tit siu7 ok-po3, -- khoaN3 Lou7-ka XVI sou2 ki3-chai3, hit-e5 ho2-giah8-lang5 kap La-sat-lou7 khi2-thau5 kap kiat-boe2 e5 su7-cheng5.
  3. U7 siuN7 hit-e5 lang5 thang chun5 hit-chit8-khou-gin5 kau3 loa7-ku2 . Hit-e5 gin5 sui-jian5 si7 beng5-beng5 ti7-teh , m7-ku2 bo5 thang eng2-oan2 khng3-teh. Lang5 chit-tiap8 sou2 u7-e5 chiN5 kau3 si2 tioh8 lau5 hou7 pat8-lang5 , chiu7 ti7 si2-au7 long2 bo5 hit-ho7 . Kho2-kian3 na7 bo5 leng7-goa7 chek-chu7 thiN--nih8 e5 chiN5-chai5 chiu7-si7 kheng5-khou2 kau3-kek8. Seng3-chheh tu2-tu2 chin-sit8 u7 kong2, “Sou2 khoaN3-kiN3--e5 si7 chiam7-si5 , sou2 be7 khoaN3-kiN3--e5 si7 ku2-tng5 .” An2-ni-seN, lan2 tioh8 te7-it-toa7 tui3-tiong7 be7 pai7-hoai7 e5 mih8, chiu7 chai7-seN si2-au7 long2 u7 thang hiong2-siu7 hok-khi3 . 
